<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3805417" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix"><p>继《血狮》之后又一国产跨时代在线对战游戏大作：《血乎》。</p><br><p>（画质感人，流量巨大，建议使用天河一号观看。）</p><br><br><p>对方大V</p><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/1136f57c5817059c04dc94391c098b63_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="330" data-rawheight="358" class="content_image" width="330"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="330" data-rawheight="358" class="content_image lazy" width="330" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/1136f57c5817059c04dc94391c098b63_b.jpg"><br><br><p>我方大V</p><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/6badd134e46c5007fdf5a373ca080fe5_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="386" data-rawheight="361" class="content_image" width="386"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="386" data-rawheight="361" class="content_image lazy" width="386" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/6badd134e46c5007fdf5a373ca080fe5_b.jpg"><br><br><p>对方乎友发动技能【谢邀】</p><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/ad907b69848b4db63dd170805720b2bf_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1800" data-rawheight="1200" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1800" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/ad907b69848b4db63dd170805720b2bf_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="1800" data-rawheight="1200" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1800" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/ad907b69848b4db63dd170805720b2bf_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/ad907b69848b4db63dd170805720b2bf_b.jpg"><br><br><p>我方乎友发动技能【谢邀】</p><noscript><img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/4594035343f5933eb8662db783a762ec_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="332" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/4594035343f5933eb8662db783a762ec_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="332" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="500" data-original="//pic1.zhimg.com/4594035343f5933eb8662db783a762ec_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic1.zhimg.com/4594035343f5933eb8662db783a762ec_b.jpg"><br><br><p>对方乎友装备武器【干货】</p><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/d4e1ed4afeae969687e34933adca43e7_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="306" data-rawheight="432" class="content_image" width="306"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="306" data-rawheight="432" class="content_image lazy" width="306" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/d4e1ed4afeae969687e34933adca43e7_b.jpg"><br><br><p>我方乎友装备武器【干货】</p><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/8f9e19fb75c3a686abda566ba8cd4585_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="441" data-rawheight="313" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="441" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/8f9e19fb75c3a686abda566ba8cd4585_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="441" data-rawheight="313" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="441" data-original="//pic2.zhimg.com/8f9e19fb75c3a686abda566ba8cd4585_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/8f9e19fb75c3a686abda566ba8cd4585_b.jpg"><br><br><p>对方公会布置战术</p><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/d0cb5dc5525ef7c899620f3e41e27c5b_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="341" data-rawheight="275" class="content_image" width="341"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="341" data-rawheight="275" class="content_image lazy" width="341" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/d0cb5dc5525ef7c899620f3e41e27c5b_b.jpg"><br><br><p>我方公会布置战术</p><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/c2f3c582557ec9283390990079eabd71_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="150" data-rawheight="150" class="content_image" width="150"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="150" data-rawheight="150" class="content_image lazy" width="150" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/c2f3c582557ec9283390990079eabd71_b.jpg"><br><br><p>对方乎友解锁成就【实名反对】</p><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/9ab19664212b909e38afa38f57fb9531_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="340" data-rawheight="210" class="content_image" width="340"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="340" data-rawheight="210"